The '''Temple of the Modeler''' was a location on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] after it was [[Terraforming/Legends|Vongformed]] into [[Coruscant/Legends#Yuuzhan'tar|Yuuzhan'tar]]. Built for the [[Shaper caste]], the temple was dedicated to [[Yun-Ne'Shel]], the Goddess of Life.

